## saga saiyan
quest.saga_saiyan_1.title=The Warrior Called Raditz
quest.saga_saiyan_1.text=Raditz, a strange space warrior, has arrived claiming to be Goku's brother. He didn't come in peace... face him to defend Earth!
quest.saga_saiyan_1.objective_1.dialog_1=Argh... So you felt that overwhelming power approaching too.  
quest.saga_saiyan_1.objective_1.dialog_2=I've already fought him. He's much stronger than he looks. We can join forces and investigate the area... but don't think I'm on your side. I just don't want this interfering with my plans.  
quest.saga_saiyan_1.objective_1.dialog_3=He's near the Dirtstone biome. If you want to try your luck, you can find him there.
quest.saga_saiyan_1.objective_4.dialog_1=Your body collapses, drained of strength. The pain is intense, but your determination never wavered. You fought to the very end, facing an enemy far beyond your limits, and even in defeat, you proved your courage. Your sacrifice was not in vain.
quest.saga_saiyan_1.objective_5.dialog_1=Your consciousness awakens in a strange place. A long path stretches out before you. This is the road to the Other World. Move forward... Enma Daioh awaits to judge your fate.
quest.saga_saiyan_1.objective_6.dialog_1=Hmph... Kami-Sama spoke very highly of you.
quest.saga_saiyan_1.objective_6.dialog_2=Because of what is yet to come, it was decided that you will keep your physical body here in the Other World.
quest.saga_saiyan_1.objective_6.dialog_3=You will be sent to Lord Kaioh's planet. The battle is not over yet. In about one year, two warriors far more powerful will arrive on Earth. Prepare yourself... the true challenge is only beginning.
quest.saga_saiyan_2.title=A New Threat Approaches
quest.saga_saiyan_2.text=After Raditz's defeat, Goku discovers that two warriors even more powerful are on their way to Earth. They will arrive in one year. Use this time to prepare!
quest.saga_saiyan_2.objective_2.dialog_1=Oh ho ho! So you're the new student Kami sent? Interesting!
quest.saga_saiyan_2.objective_2.dialog_2=Hmmm... your ki is still weak, but there is potential. I like that!
quest.saga_saiyan_2.objective_2.dialog_3=If you want to train with me, you'll need discipline... and maybe learn to understand my jokes too, ho ho ho!
quest.saga_saiyan_2.objective_4.dialog_1=Oh ho ho! Hehe… I can sense a change in your ki.
quest.saga_saiyan_2.objective_4.dialog_2=Look at that, it's more stable, more controlled. The training is starting to pay off.
quest.saga_saiyan_2.objective_4.dialog_3=Don't get too confident now! There is still much to learn. Keep training, because when
quest.saga_saiyan_2.objective_5.dialog_1=I see you've returned from the Other World... and your ki is much sharper now.
quest.saga_saiyan_2.objective_5.dialog_2=Training with Lord Kaioh is not easy. You've overcome another important step.
quest.saga_saiyan_2.objective_5.dialog_3=Keep getting stronger. The true battle draws ever closer.
quest.saga_saiyan_3.title=Green Invaders: The Saibamen
quest.saga_saiyan_3.text=Nappa and Vegeta have finally arrived! Nappa unleashes strange creatures called Saibamen to test Earth's warriors. Defeat them all!
quest.saga_saiyan_4.title=Nappa's Rampage
quest.saga_saiyan_4.text=With the Saibamen defeated, Nappa steps in and begins destroying everything in his path. Stop him before it's too late!
quest.saga_saiyan_5.title=Vegeta's Pride
quest.saga_saiyan_5.text=Now it's Vegeta's turn! The Saiyan prince has revealed his true power. This will be the toughest battle of your life!
## saga freeza
quest.saga_frieza_1.title=Invaders on Namek
quest.saga_frieza_1.text=After the brutal battle against the Saiyans, Earth was left in ruins. Many friends were lost... including Kami and Piccolo. With their deaths, the Dragon Balls vanished. However, Krillin has an idea: to search for the legendary Dragon Balls on Piccolo's home planet, Namek. Is there still hope?
quest.saga_frieza_1.objective_1.dialog_1=Krillin: Things are really bad... we've lost so many friends, and now the Dragon Balls are gone too... Kami and Piccolo are both dead.
quest.saga_frieza_1.objective_1.dialog_2=Krillin: But what if there are other Dragon Balls? I mean... Piccolo came from another planet, right? Maybe they have some there too!
quest.saga_frieza_1.objective_1.dialog_3=Krillin: King Kai told me that Kami's home planet is called Namek. If we find their Dragon Balls, maybe we can bring everyone back!
quest.saga_frieza_1.objective_1.dialog_4=Krillin: We can't waste any time. Let's go to Namek as soon as possible. If there's even a chance... we have to take it!
quest.saga_frieza_1.objective_3.dialog_1=Frieza Soldier: Hmph! These Earth worms think they can interfere with Lord Frieza's plans? Prepare to die!
quest.saga_frieza_1.objective_3.dialog_2=Frieza Soldier: This planet belongs to us now. You're not welcome here. Leave-or be destroyed!
quest.saga_frieza_2.title=Clash with Cui
quest.saga_frieza_2.text=Cui has been sent to eliminate any resistance on Namek. He underestimates you... prove him wrong!
quest.saga_frieza_3.title=The Brutal Dodoria
quest.saga_frieza_3.text=Dodoria is eliminating anyone who crosses his path. Face him before he gets more Dragon Balls!
quest.saga_frieza_4.title=Zarbon Reveals His True Form
quest.saga_frieza_4.text=Zarbon may look refined, but he hides a monstrous form. Get ready for an intense battle!
quest.saga_frieza_5.title=Arrival of the Ginyu Force
quest.saga_frieza_5.text=Frieza has summoned his elite squad! Defeat Guldo and Recoome to keep advancing.
quest.saga_frieza_6.title=Burter and Jeice Strike
quest.saga_frieza_6.text=The fast duo from the Ginyu Force has arrived. Show them you're faster and stronger!
quest.saga_frieza_7.title=Captain Ginyu and the Body Swap
quest.saga_frieza_7.text=Captain Ginyu uses a dangerous technique to switch bodies with his opponents. Beat him before he uses it on you!
quest.saga_frieza_8.title=Frieza's Wrath
quest.saga_frieza_8.text=With his squad defeated, Frieza has decided to fight personally. Prepare to face his true power!
quest.saga_frieza_9.title=Final Form: Frieza
quest.saga_frieza_9.text=Frieza has reached his final form! This is the hardest battle of your life, don't lose control now!
quest.saga_frieza_10.title=The Emperor's Soldiers
quest.saga_frieza_10.text=Frieza and his father, King Cold, have arrived on Earth with a new army. Before facing them directly, defeat the soldiers threatening the citizens!
quest.saga_frieza_11.title=Return of Frieza and King Cold
quest.saga_frieza_11.text=After eliminating their soldiers, Frieza reveals his plan: destroy Earth! Face King Cold and prepare for the final clash with Frieza!
quest.saga_frieza_12.title=End of the Threat
quest.saga_frieza_12.text=The time has come to end Frieza once and for all. This is your chance to protect Earth. Fight with everything you've got!
## saga android
quest.saga_android_1.title=A Terrifying Future
quest.saga_android_1.text=Trunks came from the future with a dark warning: in a few years, killer androids will appear and destroy everything. Get ready!
quest.saga_android_2.title=Clash with Androids 19 and 20
quest.saga_android_2.text=Androids 19 and 20 have appeared and are wreaking havoc in the city. Stop them before it's too late!
quest.saga_android_3.title=Duel with Android 17
quest.saga_android_3.text=After the first androids were defeated, Dr. Gero released two more: 17 and 18. Android 17 is eliminating anyone in his way. Face him with all you've got!
quest.saga_android_4.title=Facing Android 18
quest.saga_android_4.text=Android 18 has shown her strength against the Z fighters. She's cold, calculated, and extremely powerful. Get ready for battle!
quest.saga_android_5.title=The Perfect Monster
quest.saga_android_5.text=A new enemy has appeared: Cell, a bio-android created to absorb the others. He's on the loose. Stop him before he reaches his perfect form!
## saga majin
quest.saga_majin_1.title=Pui Pui, the Warrior from Zoon
quest.saga_majin_1.text=The wizard Babidi has begun his plan to release Majin Buu by gathering energy through battles aboard his ship. His first defender is Pui Pui from the planet Zoon. Overcome this challenge to keep moving forward!
quest.saga_majin_2.title=Yakon, the Light Devourer
quest.saga_majin_2.text=Yakon feeds on the light energy of his opponents. Fight smart and stop him from draining your power!
quest.saga_majin_3.title=Dabura, King of the Demons
quest.saga_majin_3.text=Dabura, Babidi's strongest commander, awaits you. He's cruel and relentless. Defeat him to ruin the wizard's plans!
quest.saga_majin_4.title=Majin Vegeta
quest.saga_majin_4.text=Controlled by Babidi, Vegeta has unleashed all his pride and power. This fight is more than a battle. It's a reckoning.
quest.saga_majin_5.title=The Awakening of Majin Buu
quest.saga_majin_5.text=Babidi did it! Majin Buu has been released. Despite his childish look, he's a devastating threat that must be stopped immediately.
quest.saga_majin_6.title=Super Buu, Rising Fury
quest.saga_majin_6.text=After absorbing powerful warriors, Majin Buu evolved into an even more destructive form. This will be your toughest battle yet.
quest.saga_majin_7.title=Kid Buu, Pure Evil
quest.saga_majin_7.text=Kid Buu is the original and most dangerous form of Majin Buu-chaotic, merciless, and unpredictable. The final battle for the universe begins now!
## saga beerus
quest.saga_beerus_1.title=The Awakening of Beerus
quest.saga_beerus_1.text=After a long slumber, the God of Destruction, Beerus, awakened with a strange premonition: a being of incredible power may soon emerge. He has arrived on Earth in search of this warrior...
quest.saga_beerus_1.objective_1.dialog_1=Oh, are you the warrior we've been looking for? Certainly not. Your ki is far from divine and nowhere near Beerus's level...
quest.saga_beerus_1.objective_1.dialog_2=He's furious. Perhaps destroying this planet will calm him down. You'd better find that powerful being-fast!
quest.saga_beerus_1.objective_4.dialog_1=I must admit, the skill you possess seems limitless.
quest.saga_beerus_1.objective_4.dialog_2=However, I wouldn't call you my archrival... Farewell!
## saga freeza dourado
quest.saga_golden_frieza_1.title=The Return of an Old Enemy
quest.saga_golden_frieza_1.text=Frieza has been resurrected by his followers and is training for revenge. Prepare yourself for the chaos that lies ahead!
quest.saga_golden_frieza_2.title=Frieza's Army Attacks
quest.saga_golden_frieza_2.text=With a new army, Frieza begins his offensive. Face his soldiers while he prepares for the final strike!
quest.saga_golden_frieza_3.title=Tagoma and Shisame
quest.saga_golden_frieza_3.text=Two loyal warriors of Frieza are destroying cities in his name. Confront them and stop further destruction!
quest.saga_golden_frieza_4.title=Golden Frieza
quest.saga_golden_frieza_4.text=Frieza has mastered a new form: the Golden Form. His power is immense. This will be a battle like no other!
## saga universo 6
quest.saga_universe_6_1.title=The Tournament of Universes
quest.saga_universe_6_1.text=The God of Destruction Champa has issued a challenge: a tournament between the best warriors of Universes 6 and 7! You've been chosen to represent your universe. Before the battle begins, train with the Z Fighters and prove you're worthy of this legendary clash!
quest.saga_universe_6_1.objective_1.dialog_1=This tournament won't be like any fight you've faced before.
quest.saga_universe_6_1.objective_1.dialog_2=You need to learn to stay calm and analyze every enemy move.
quest.saga_universe_6_1.objective_1.dialog_3=Let's train your technique and awareness. Attack me when you're ready!
quest.saga_universe_6_1.objective_3.dialog_1=Hehe, so you're joining the tournament too? That's awesome!
quest.saga_universe_6_1.objective_3.dialog_2=But hey, the Universe 6 guys aren't pushovers. You'll have to give it your all!
quest.saga_universe_6_1.objective_3.dialog_3=Let's train a bit. I want to see if you can handle a real fight with me!
quest.saga_universe_6_1.objective_5.dialog_1=Nice job! Now get ready... the tournament is about to begin!
quest.saga_universe_6_2.title=Botamo, the Rubber Bear
quest.saga_universe_6_2.text=Your first opponent is Botamo. He can absorb physical attacks like he doesn't feel pain. Use strategy to defeat him!
quest.saga_universe_6_3.title=Frost, the "Hero" of Universe 6
quest.saga_universe_6_3.text=Frost seems noble, but he hides dark intentions. Fight carefully so you don't fall for his tricks!
quest.saga_universe_6_4.title=Magetta, the Lava Warrior
quest.saga_universe_6_4.text=Magetta's hot metallic body can destabilize anyone. Use your endurance to overcome him!
quest.saga_universe_6_5.title=Cabba, the Young Saiyan
quest.saga_universe_6_5.text=Cabba is a Saiyan from Universe 6 with a pure heart and great power. Show him the true pride of the Saiyans!
quest.saga_universe_6_6.title=Hit, the Legendary Assassin
quest.saga_universe_6_6.text=Hit has mastered time-skip techniques that challenge even the gods. Push beyond the limits of time to defeat him!





## missões secundárias
## battle jacket return
quest.battle_jacket_return.title=Red Ribbon Remnants
quest.battle_jacket_return.text=A war machine from the old Red Ribbon Army has been spotted active again. It seems to be patrolling the plains, looking for something... or someone. Investigate and destroy the threat before it causes any damage.
quest.battle_jacket_return.dialog_1=Something strange is going on... an old Red Ribbon unit is operating on its own.
quest.battle_jacket_return.dialog_2=It's been seen in the plains, firing energy blasts at anything that gets too close.
quest.battle_jacket_return.dialog_3=Maybe it's a leftover from Dr. Gero. Either way, it must be stopped.
quest.battle_jacket_return.objective_2.dialog_1=So it was still active... Incredible that it lasted this long.
quest.battle_jacket_return.objective_2.dialog_2=You defeated it? Excellent. Red Ribbon never learns, huh?
quest.battle_jacket_return.objective_2.dialog_3=Stay alert. Where there's one machine like that, there might be more.
## bring fish for karin
quest.bring_fish_for_karin.title=Fish for a Cloud
quest.bring_fish_for_karin.text=Meow! I see you're looking for a faster way to travel, huh? I can give you one of my flying clouds, but first... can you bring me some fish?
quest.bring_fish_for_karin.dialog_1=Meow... I see you're still not quite used to flying.
quest.bring_fish_for_karin.dialog_2=Climbing up here isn't something just anyone can do. But maybe you're ready...
quest.bring_fish_for_karin.dialog_3=Bring me some fresh fish, and perhaps I'll share one of my Flying Clouds with you.
quest.bring_fish_for_karin.objective_2.dialog_1=Meow... What a delightful smell! You really brought some fine fish.
quest.bring_fish_for_karin.objective_2.dialog_2=I see potential in you. And good taste in food too, hehe.
quest.bring_fish_for_karin.objective_2.dialog_3=As promised, here's one of my Flying Nimbuses. Take good care of it… not everyone can ride one.
## fetch bulma outfit
quest.fetch_bulma_outfit.title=The Perverted Old Man
quest.fetch_bulma_outfit.text=Hohoho! So you've come to my house? Very well! You want to be my student, huh? Well, not just anyone can be trained by me... but I'll consider it if you bring me a little something first, hehe!
quest.fetch_bulma_outfit.dialog_1=Hehehe... It's been a while since I had a visitor like this!
quest.fetch_bulma_outfit.dialog_2=You want to be my student? Hah! You'll have to impress me first.
quest.fetch_bulma_outfit.dialog_3=Bring me something... special. An outfit from Bulma would be perfect, hohoho!
## piccolo trial
quest.piccolo_trial.title=Piccolo's Challenge
quest.piccolo_trial.text=Hmph... you want me to teach you one of my techniques? Then prove your worth now. I have no time for indecisive warriors. If you can't defeat me quickly, you don't even deserve to hear its name.
## pirate robot treasure
quest.pirate_robot_treasure.title=Iron Pirate's Treasure
quest.pirate_robot_treasure.text=They say an old pirate built a mechanical body to extend his life and guard his treasure. He was last seen wandering a remote coast... maybe there's something valuable hidden there.
quest.pirate_robot_treasure.dialog_1=Hey... I've heard rumors about a pirate robot that appears on beaches at night.
quest.pirate_robot_treasure.dialog_2=He's said to guard a buried chest containing ancient artifacts.
quest.pirate_robot_treasure.dialog_3=If you want to try your luck, head to a coastal biome. But be careful... he doesn't like visitors.
quest.pirate_robot_treasure.objective_3.dialog_1=So you faced the Pirate Robot? Impressive!
quest.pirate_robot_treasure.objective_3.dialog_2=Maybe that treasure holds more secrets than we thought...
quest.pirate_robot_treasure.objective_3.dialog_3=Use what you found wisely. Not all power comes from fighting.
## saibaman challenge
quest.saibaman_challenge.title=Saibaman Trial
quest.saibaman_challenge.text=Saibamen have begun appearing in large numbers, attacking anyone who gets close. Simple creatures, created only to fight until death. Each wave feels more aggressive than the last. Hold your ground and eliminate them all before the situation spirals out of control.
quest.saibaman_challenge.dialog_1=Saibamen... appearing out of nowhere.
quest.saibaman_challenge.dialog_2=They don't retreat, they don't think. They only attack.
quest.saibaman_challenge.dialog_3=If I fall here, I'll be just another body on the ground.
## train with goku
quest.train_with_goku.title=Let's Train!
quest.train_with_goku.text=Hey! I sensed your ki from far away... you seem strong! How about we train a bit? I promise I won't go all out-unless you can handle it, hehe!
quest.train_with_goku.dialog_1=Hi! I sensed an interesting ki coming from around here.
quest.train_with_goku.dialog_2=You look strong! How about a friendly sparring match to warm up?
quest.train_with_goku.dialog_3=Don't worry, I'll go easy on you... at first!
## visit lookout
quest.visit_lookout.title=Stairway to the Sky
quest.visit_lookout.text=They say Master Karin watches over the world from a place high above the clouds. If you're worthy, maybe you'll reach it. Head to coordinates X:150 Z:150 and see what awaits you at the top.
quest.visit_lookout.objective_1.dialog_1=They say someone watches over the world from high above the clouds...
quest.visit_lookout.objective_1.dialog_2=Not everyone can reach such a place. But maybe you have what it takes.
quest.visit_lookout.objective_1.dialog_3=Head to the marked spot... and climb. The truth awaits above.
quest.visit_lookout.objective_3.dialog_1=Oh? So you actually made it up here... not bad for a beginner.
quest.visit_lookout.objective_3.dialog_2=I am Master Korin. Many try to reach me, but few succeed.
quest.visit_lookout.objective_3.dialog_3=If you're here seeking power, you'll need more than strong legs... Prove yourself worthy.
## whis ramen delivery
quest.whis_ramen_delivery.title=Divine Appetite
quest.whis_ramen_delivery.text=Oh? You wish to train with me? How curious. But before we begin any instruction, I must confess something: I've heard quite a bit about your planet's unique delicacies. There's one dish that caught my attention... what was it called again? Ramen? Yes, that's it! A warm, fragrant broth full of flavor. Bring me two bowls, one for myself, and one for Lord Beerus. If they manage to please our divine palates, I might just feel inspired to train you. How about that?
quest.whis_ramen_delivery.dialog_1=Oh? A curious mortal approaches... What a delightful surprise.
quest.whis_ramen_delivery.dialog_2=I am Whis, attendant and master of the God of Destruction. Charmed, I suppose.
quest.whis_ramen_delivery.dialog_3=Seeking power, are you? How predictable... yet still intriguing.
quest.whis_ramen_delivery.dialog_4=Very well... Before we talk about training, how about something tasty to whet my appetite?
quest.whis_ramen_delivery.objective_2.dialog_1=Ohh... What a wonderful aroma! This ramen looks worthy of a divine banquet.
quest.whis_ramen_delivery.objective_2.dialog_2=Excellent presentation! One for me... and the other, of course, for Lord Beerus. How delightful!
quest.whis_ramen_delivery.objective_2.dialog_3=Splendid. You truly know how to please. A refined taste is a good start, and it will serve you well in the training ahead.
## world connections
quest.world_connections.title=Bonds of a Living World
quest.world_connections.text=This world is made of battles, but also of encounters. Every person you meet, every word exchanged, leaves an invisible mark on destiny. Before moving forward, walk through this world... and meet everyone who makes it alive.
quest.world_connections.dialog_1=Oh? So you made it this far.
quest.world_connections.dialog_2=You know, when I created this world, I didn't think only about fights.
quest.world_connections.dialog_3=I thought about people. About how every encounter changes someone.
quest.world_connections.dialog_4=If you truly want to understand this universe, go talk to everyone.
quest.world_connections.dialog_5=Don't fight. Don't run. Just get to know them.
quest.world_connections.objective_2.dialog_1=I see that you found all of them.
quest.world_connections.objective_2.dialog_2=Warriors, gods, monsters, ordinary people.
quest.world_connections.objective_2.dialog_3=They are all part of the same story.
quest.world_connections.objective_2.dialog_4=Thank you for walking through this world with respect.
quest.world_connections.objective_2.dialog_5=As long as someone remembers them, this world will remain alive.





